.org/resource/Denmark_national_football_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a score\", \"from\": 932, \"to\": 939}, {\"ngram\": \"cent\", \"from\": 954, \"to\": 958}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The bronze medal comes after a testing period for the British equestrian team, with three-time dressage gold-medal winnerCharlotte Dujardinhaving withdrawn from the Games just days before the opening ceremony, meaning reserve rider Moody stepped into the team.\", \"from\": 1023, \"to\": 1283, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1255, \"end\": 1260, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Moody's_Investors_Service\", \"score\": 0.8165870239403483, \"rank\": 0.2227430713196086, \"text\": \"Moody\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Moody's_Investors_Service\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Moody's_Investors_Service\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The bronze medal\", \"from\": 1023, \"to\": 1039}, {\"ngram\": \"a testing period\", \"from\": 1052, \"to\": 1068}, {\"ngram\": \"the British equestrian team\", \"from\": 1073, \"to\": 1100}, {\"ngram\": \"three-time dressage gold-medal winnerCharlotte Dujardinhaving\", \"from\": 1107, \"to\": 1168}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 1184, \"to\": 1193}, {\"ngram\": \"the opening ceremony\", \"from\": 1211, \"to\": 1231}, {\"ngram\": \"reserve rider\", \"from\": 1241, \"to\": 1254}, {\"ngram\": \"the team\", \"from\": 1274, \"to\": 1282}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Dujardin dropped out of Paris and was provisionally suspendedby equestrian's governing body, the International Federation for Equestrian Sports (FEI), pending an investigation into a video from four years ago which showed her repeatedly hitting a student's horse with a whip from the ground during a coaching session.\", \"from\": 1285, \"to\": 1602, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1309, \"end\": 1314, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.999999999956799, \"rank\": 4.3207216581304465e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 1349, \"end\": 1359, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Equestrianism\", \"score\": 0.5680189349294071, \"rank\": 0.7605046914501088, \"text\": \"equestrian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Equestrianism\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Equestrianism\"}, {\"begin\": 1430, \"end\": 1433, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Federation_for_Equestrian_Sports\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.581346398800659e-32, \"text\": \"FEI\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Federation_for_Equestrian_Sports\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Federation_for_Equestrian_Sports\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the International Federation\", \"from\": 1378, \"to\": 1406}, {\"ngram\": \"Equestrian Sports\", \"from\": 1411, \"to\": 1428}, {\"ngram\": \"an investigation\", \"from\": 1444, \"to\": 1460}, {\"ngram\": \"a video\", \"from\": 1466, \"to\": 1473}, {\"ngram\": \"a student's horse\", \"from\": 1530, \"to\": 1547}, {\"ngram\": \"a whip\", \"from\": 1553, \"to\": 1559}, {\"ngram\": \"the ground\", \"from\": 1565, \"to\": 1575}, {\"ngram\": \"a coaching session\", \"from\": 1583, \"to\": 1601}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Hester, who enjoyed a long relationship with Dujardin as her mentor, said: \\\"It's been really difficult, very hard, and as I said before, we have had to put it out of our minds.\", \"from\": 1604, \"to\": 1780, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Hester\", \"from\": 1604, \"to\": 1610}, {\"ngram\": \"a long relationship\", \"from\": 1624, \"to\": 1643}, {\"ngram\": \"Dujardin\", \"from\": 1649, \"to\": 1657}, {\"ngram\": \"her mentor\", \"from\": 1661, \"to\": 1671}, {\"ngram\": \"our minds\", \"from\": 1770, \"to\": 1779}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I have had to concentrate on the team and I am lucky in a way that I had Becky to deal with every day and help, which helps me focus on something else.\", \"from\": 1782, \"to\": 1934, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the team\", \"from\": 1812, \"to\": 1820}, {\"ngram\": \"a way\", \"from\": 1839, \"to\": 1844}, {\"ngram\": \"Becky\", \"from\": 1856, \"to\": 1861}, {\"ngram\": \"every day\", \"from\": 1875, \"to\": 1884}, {\"ngram\": \"help\", \"from\": 1889, \"to\": 1893}, {\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 1919, \"to\": 1928}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We have full-time jobs most of us, then you come here and you have one horse to ride and you are just going out of your mind with what not to think about all day and what to do all day.\", \"from\": 1936, \"to\": 2122, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"full-time jobs\", \"from\": 1945, \"to\": 1959}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 1968, \"to\": 1970}, {\"ngram\": \"one horse\", \"from\": 2004, \"to\": 2013}, {\"ngram\": \"your mind\", \"from\": 2052, \"to\": 2061}, {\"ngram\": \"all day\", \"from\": 2091, \"to\": 2098}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's been a long week but I feel fantastic now it's done.\\\"\", \"from\": 2124, \"to\": 2183, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"While Hester was appearing at his seventhOlympics, Moody was enjoying a dream debut with her gelding Jagerbomb, who she bred herself.\", \"from\": 2185, \"to\": 2318, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2191, \"end\": 2197, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hester_Thrale\", \"score\": 0.9948961100265757, \"rank\": 0.005130073302979687, \"text\": \"Hester\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hester_Thrale\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hester_Thrale\"}, {\"begin\": 2236, \"end\": 2241, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Moody's_Investors_Service\", \"score\": 0.8165870239403483, \"rank\": 0.2227430713196086, \"text\": \"Moody\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Moody's_Investors_Service\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Moody's_Investors_Service\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his seventhOlympics\", \"from\": 2215, \"to\": 2234}, {\"ngram\": \"a dream debut\", \"from\": 2255, \"to\": 2268}, {\"ngram\": \"her gelding Jagerbomb\", \"from\": 2274, \"to\": 2295}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She said: \\\"What an incredible stadium and the crowd were fantastic and my horse was a total legend.\", \"from\": 2320, \"to\": 2419, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"What an incredible stadium\", \"from\": 2331, \"to\": 2357}, {\"ngram\": \"the crowd\", \"from\": 2362, \"to\": 2371}, {\"ngram\": \"my horse\", \"from\": 2391, \"to\": 2399}, {\"ngram\": \"a total legend\", \"from\": 2404, \"to\": 2418}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I think because I bred him and we have done everything together, he's just a total dude - a lovely, lovely horse.\", \"from\": 2421, \"to\": 2535, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"everything\", \"from\": 2466, \"to\": 2476}, {\"ngram\": \"a total dude\", \"from\": 2497, \"to\": 2509}, {\"ngram\": \"a lovely, lovely horse\", \"from\": 2512, \"to\": 2534}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"He's been quite spicy here this week and Carl has helped me out an awful lot to find that inner calm in both of us, but it has been fantastic and he's been amazing.\\\"\", \"from\": 2537, \"to\": 2703, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Carl\", \"from\": 2579, \"to\": 2583}, {\"ngram\": \"an awful lot\", \"from\": 2602, \"to\": 2614}, {\"ngram\": \"that inner calm\", \"from\": 2623, \"to\": 2638}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 2650, \"to\": 2652}]}, {\"sentence\": \"MORE ABOUT Have your say... 1 Crime Fight breaks out on Elizabeth line train after youths told to stop vaping by middle-aged passenger Fight breaks out on Elizabeth line after youths told to stop vaping 2 Football Liverpool XI vs Brighton: Sta